Package GoNature

Class Traveler

  • java.lang.Object
    • GoNature.Traveler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class Traveler
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The Traveler class represents a traveler who may have booked visits to parks. It stores information such as name, ID, email, phone number, and authority level. This class provides methods to retrieve and modify traveler details.
    Author:
    Pier Mbariky, Redan Ganim, Bassel Haddad, Joel Hourany, Asaad Sajim, Nadine Halabi
    See Also:
